headline: Teradyne to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Results
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., January 13, 2026--Teradyne, Inc. (NASDAQ: TER) will release financial results for the fourth quarter and full year 2025 on Monday, February 2, 2026 at 5:00 p.m. Eastern Time (ET) or later.
